                                                 THEMIS

        A Software to Assess Association Free Energies via Direct Estimative of Partion Function

                                       Author: Felippe M. Colombari
                                                 Brazil

                                         Program version: 1.0.0
                                           Revision: ae2e8ac
  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Contributions
       Asdrubal Lozada: Error handling revision

    This version of THEMIS uses:
       SPHERE_GRID library (John Burkardt)
       XDR library (James Barnett)

       For citations, please refer to:
         https://people.sc.fsu.edu/~jburkardt/f_src/sphere_grid/sphere_grid.html
         https://github.com/kmtu/xdrfort/blob/master/xdr.F90

  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    COMMAND LINE READ: ./themis --help

            Usage:  themis [RUNTYPE] [GRIDTYPE] [RADIUS|FILENAME]     

  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

                              [RUNTYPE] options

              --run               Start new calculation.

            --rerun               Calculate properties from energies previously calculated:
                                  energy.bin file - from Themis run;
                                  energy.log file - from external calculation.

  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

                             [GRIDTYPE] options

            --shell               Translation moves will be performed on a spherical shell
                                  of radius RADIUS generated on the run.

             --user               Translation moves will be performed on an user-defined
                                  grid read from FILENAME.
  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

                               [RADIUS] value

             (real)               Scaling factor for the spherical grid radius (in Angstrom)

                             [FILENAME] value

             (char)               XYZ file containing the user-defined translation grid. It
                                  must be aligned with molecule 1

  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

                                Other options

             --help               Display this help

          --version               Display the version

  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Sucessfull termination.
